---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
---

<Layout title="行事曆 | 光禾華德福">
  <Navigation />
  
  <section class="hero-small">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>行事曆</h1>
      <p>光禾家長行事曆</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      
      <div class="calendar-intro">
        <p>📅 114學年度 春學季</p>
        <p class="note">以下為Google行事曆，可以直接同步到您的 Google 行事曆</p>
        <a href="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/r?cid=YOUR_CALENDAR_ID" target="_blank" class="btn-add">
          ➕ 加入 Google 行事曆
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Google Calendar Embed -->
      <div class="calendar-embed">
        <iframe 
          src="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/embed?src=YOUR_CALENDAR_ID&ctz=Asia/Taipei" 
          style="border: 0" 
          width="100%" 
          height="600" 
          frameborder="0" 
          scrolling="no">
        </iframe>
      </div>

      <div class="month-section">
        <h2 class="month-title">🌸 三月 2026</h2>
        
        <div class="event-list">
          <div class="event-item">
            <div class="event-date">
              <span class="day">3-4</span>
              <span class="week">週二-三</span>
            </div>
            <div class="event-content">
              <h3>G9茉莉班第三次會考模擬考</h3>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="event-item highlight">
            <div class="event-date">
              <span class="day">14</span>
              <span class="week">週六</span>
            </div>
            <div class="event-content">
              <h3>114春季聯合班親會</h3>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="event-item highlight">
            <div class="event-date">
              <span class="day">21</span>
              <span class="week">週六</span>
            </div>
            <div class="event-content">
              <h3>115學年度春季招生說明會</h3>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="event-item highlight">
            <div class="event-date">
              <span class="day">28</span>
              <span class="week">週六</span>
            </div>
            <div class="event-content">
              <h3>114春季慶典暨校慶</h3>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="event-item holiday">
            <div class="event-date">
              <span class="day">3</span>
              <span class="week">週五</span>
            </div>
            <div class="event-content">
              <h3>清明節連假開始</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="note">
        <p>📌 以上時間僅供參考，實際活動日期請以學校公告為主。</p>
        <p>如有疑問，請致電 07-7885128 詢問。</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <p>© 2026 光禾華德福實驗學校. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-small {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B4513, #228B22);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-small h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .hero-small p { font-size: 1.2rem; opacity: 0.9; }

  .section { padding: 4rem 2rem; }
  .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .calendar-intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .calendar-intro p {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #228B22;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .calendar-intro .note {
    display: block;
    background: none;
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .btn-add {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #4285f4;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 25px;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-add:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .calendar-embed {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(139,69,19,0.1);
  }

  .month-section {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(139,69,19,0.1);
  }

  .month-title {
    color: #8B4513;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e0d4c8;
  }

  .event-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .event-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 15px;
    background: #f9f9f9;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .event-item:hover {
    transform: translateX(5px);
  }

  .event-item.highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e9, #fff);
    border-left: 4px solid #228B22;
  }

  .event-item.holiday {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3e0, #fff);
    border-left: 4px solid #ff9800;
  }

  .event-date {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-width: 60px;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    background: #8B4513;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  .event-date .day {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .event-date .week {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .event-content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .event-content h3 {
    color: #555;
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .note {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: #f5f5f5;
    border-radius: 15px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .note p {
    color: #666;
    margin: 0.3rem 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .footer { background: #333; color: white; padding: 2rem; text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; }
</style>
